{"tid":169043,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳展鵬偷戀落選港姐 胡定欣怨上錯賊船","createTime":"2017-03-24T02:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T03:19:24.000Z","uid":9573,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"62016b1d4152cc1d786da5ce007f2b33255917de","tid":169043,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T02:57:54.000Z","msg":"陳展鵬 (煎Pang) 與胡定欣拍《城寨英雄》時撻着，人前人後sweet到爆，早被認定為一對。不過早前40歲煎Pang帶住下月27歲落選港姐單文柔摸黑上山頂，被當場斷正！為免被標籤成負心漢，煎Pang急撇清關係：「我從來冇同胡定欣拍拖」，一刀插入定欣心坎。頓覺癡心錯付的定欣，自責無帶眼識人，近日收工孤伶一人，只有助手陪食，顯得落寞非常﹗女人有車有樓有事業，感情屢遇挫折，好傷﹗<br />\n <br />\n「你想去邊我都陪你﹗」<br />\n上星期煎Pang定欣孖住出席影視展，訪問時當眾打情罵俏，定欣指恨拍旅遊節目，記者問想去邊？定欣心心眼望住展鵬問：「你想去邊？」煎Pang甜爆回話：「你想去邊我都陪你﹗」定欣登時被電到暈陀陀，笑到花枝招展。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3.yimg.com/bt/api/res/1.2/WdExsrma3T8Aiof1l_uw3Q--/YXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9MzEw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/orientalsundayent.com/0d622bf4082b1e466da31041afe38674\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.yimg.com%2Fbt%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FWdExsrma3T8Aiof1l_uw3Q--%2FYXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9MzEw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Forientalsundayent.com%2F0d622bf4082b1e466da31041afe38674&h=92d32d52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s3.yimg.com/bt/api/res/1.2/rhzh160vW41spIdd8EVRRA--/YXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9MzEw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/orientalsundayent.com/989fe86211483a147711f6320f547758\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.yimg.com%2Fbt%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Frhzh160vW41spIdd8EVRRA--%2FYXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9MzEw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Forientalsundayent.com%2F989fe86211483a147711f6320f547758&h=d81a45c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n山頂密會斷正<br />\n不過在定欣出發吉隆坡拍廣告後，煎Pang就被被斷正與16年落選港姐單文柔密會，兩人摸黑上山頂歎外賣！當記者上前影相時，煎Pang表現驚慌，左掩右遮，反而女方較為鎮定，碌大眼望向鏡頭。方寸大亂的煎Pang開車速逃，倒車時更撞向後面的採訪車。事後煎Pang聲稱定欣只是同事，二人從來冇拍過拖，同時亦打死唔肯認新女單文柔：「佢係我stylist，嗰日佢幫我揀啲衫褲登台，要好多謝佢免費幫我。(點解上山頂傾？) 幫襯開嘅餐廳冇位，又冇地方泊車所以喺車傾囉。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://s2.yimg.com/bt/api/res/1.2/d.QiVFR.BdBrG7h6Om_Klg--/YXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9MzEw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/orientalsundayent.com/f4e160ad3d6b2494c5760ed188a3c4b3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs2.yimg.com%2Fbt%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fd.QiVFR.BdBrG7h6Om_Klg--%2FYXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9MzEw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Forientalsundayent.com%2Ff4e160ad3d6b2494c5760ed188a3c4b3&h=f1a256b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n愁爆食tea<br />\n定欣和煎Pang早已是外界認定的一對，但突然傳出煎Pang竟然有個女友單文柔，難怪定欣咁傷心。唔使開工的日子，好姊妹又個個忙拍劇，定欣就與助手去鯉景灣食tea，不過見到佢一臉落寞，全程冇笑容，睇嚟心情相當差。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/bt/api/res/1.2/RT214GIL1x_FkjXoahluog--/YXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9MzEw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/orientalsundayent.com/4286486b67aa15153c24f16ef8d5f5a0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fbt%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FRT214GIL1x_FkjXoahluog--%2FYXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9MzEw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Forientalsundayent.com%2F4286486b67aa15153c24f16ef8d5f5a0&h=d3e8c4e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s2.yimg.com/bt/api/res/1.2/j8qgINWDWyKROlKzVq1Vqg--/YXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9MzEw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/orientalsundayent.com/85aeea26b002b9ae8e42f020141e47a6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs2.yimg.com%2Fbt%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fj8qgINWDWyKROlKzVq1Vqg--%2FYXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9MzEw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Forientalsundayent.com%2F85aeea26b002b9ae8e42f020141e47a6&h=6cfdbbe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n煎Pang一拖二同場<br />\n今年一月時，無綫拉隊參加公益金百萬行，出爐視帝視后煎Pang、定欣領隊參與，當時已經和單文柔拍拖的煎Pang做戲做全套，全程同定欣孖公仔，不時舉機跟定欣自拍，定欣冧爆挨實。單文柔等代表港姐出席，一男兩女來個大合照，真係一家親。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.yimg.com/bt/api/res/1.2/riwOlAgdRwFF_HZ300SU.w--/YXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9MzEw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/orientalsundayent.com/06df469e9f08a454e1ec4ad86ba0c306\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.yimg.com%2Fbt%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FriwOlAgdRwFF_HZ300SU.w--%2FYXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9MzEw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Forientalsundayent.com%2F06df469e9f08a454e1ec4ad86ba0c306&h=d200e8d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後農曆年初四，煎Pang和定欣結伴到無綫高層樂易玲屋企拜年，當時一眾港姐包括單文柔亦在場。當港姐們不時搵視后定欣集郵，惟獨單文柔一直在屋外露天花園跟其他人自拍及聊天，煎Pang安排兩女同場，兩頭瞞認真膽大包天！<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.yimg.com/bt/api/res/1.2/uHPDHkpvZWC6RjmNw9Ne3A--/YXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9MzEw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/orientalsundayent.com/8cde2f157397c5698d9f9a04368f65aa\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.yimg.com%2Fbt%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FuHPDHkpvZWC6RjmNw9Ne3A--%2FYXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9MzEw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Forientalsundayent.com%2F8cde2f157397c5698d9f9a04368f65aa&h=264016c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好姊妹力撐<br />\n可憐的定欣上錯賊船，幸好有「胡說八道會」一班好姊妹全力支持，據知杏兒睇到煎Pang單新聞後好嬲，即時撇低老公去開解定欣。當初定欣煎Pang互有好感，定欣亦體諒對方比較慢熱，工作又真係好忙，所以唔介意慢慢發展。點知煎Pang原來暗地裏媾緊個港姐，定欣怨自己蠢上錯賊船，杏兒見狀都戥佢唔抵，同班姊妹喺背後鬧爆賤男！<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3.yimg.com/bt/api/res/1.2/CDxT.G.uf0J.zz210L1SSA--/YXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9MzEw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/orientalsundayent.com/49e4c0fc52383ed7c73675167fdc19ae\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.yimg.com%2Fbt%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FCDxT.G.uf0J.zz210L1SSA--%2FYXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9MzEw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Forientalsundayent.com%2F49e4c0fc52383ed7c73675167fdc19ae&h=a84ccd27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/bt/api/res/1.2/dDHG4ZgAoiZN8VNUiPrvnw--/YXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9MzEw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/orientalsundayent.com/c1ac4d39bc5df6c06fe6f4178c402a15\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fbt%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FdDHG4ZgAoiZN8VNUiPrvnw--%2FYXBwaWQ9eW5ld3NfbGVnbztxPTg1O3c9MzEw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Forientalsundayent.com%2Fc1ac4d39bc5df6c06fe6f4178c402a15&h=50a78973&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"246ec378087e14aeae115ef6e8055a54ff18113c","tid":169043,"uid":54576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67197ab11e396f0168ed91ab394a43161bd927b","tid":169043,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T03:26:45.000Z","msg":"亞視暗星一過檔變一哥"},{"pid":"2c79800fa34dd75c9824889b5abb517b67859f43","tid":169043,"uid":7878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T04:11:06.000Z","msg":"胡說八道會<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ziines.com/ziines-user-upload/upload/2016/09/28/29040_20160928151729_57eb6e8944818.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ziines.com%2Fziines-user-upload%2Fupload%2F2016%2F09%2F28%2F29040_20160928151729_57eb6e8944818.gif&h=34aef6b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f472ef5c10109bc82d22df306b0806211974fa0c","tid":169043,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T04:40:51.000Z","msg":"乜有戀過咩？<br />\n我覺得之前只係做戲博宣傳。"},{"pid":"a1a17050246cd6955efb0780ba0d09cdb3ff19fc","tid":169043,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T04:44:01.000Z","msg":"難分真與假"},{"pid":"7e41677f9801d21fcae03a723fab13503b453e91","tid":169043,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T04:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06488826d95ad53152aa67f02c1d590d07926eb","tid":169043,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T05:09:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>胡說八道會<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ziines.com/ziines-user-upload